snippet.title: Starmancer Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Live now on Kickstarter. 

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1424711375/1744392556?ref=361421&token=bcdd2dd8


Starmancer is a Dwarf-Fortress inspired space station building game.

After a catastrophe on Earth, humanity launches the Starmancer Initiative. You are a Starmancer.


Once again, Starmancer is currently live on Kickstarter. Pre-order and add yourself to the game as a colonist.

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1424711375/1744392556?ref=361421&token=bcdd2dd8
